data.description: Welcome to your midcentury modern oasis! This 4-bed, 1.5-bath home on a large corner lot offers endless potential. Spacious rooms await your personal touch, complemented by a slate floor entry and a captivating stone fireplace. Relax in the screened porch or unleash your creativity in the expansive unfinished basement. With a single stall attached garage, convenience meets style. Your dream home awaits - seize the opportunity today!
